{"type":"message","id":"945d879b","parentId":"a2cbf379","timestamp":"2026-04-19T03:30:24.927Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now let me create the tasks.md file with all the tasks that need to be done.","thinkingSignature":"88a7670a2a0d487f50e4cd82ad184f1162d5ea702df8b2cfb182eaf780f24af4"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5ezfp03d63rl_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-knowledge-hub/openspec/changes/tech-blog/tasks.md","content":"# OpenSpec Tasks: AHV Tech Knowledge Hub\n\n**Project:** ahv-knowledge-hub  \n**Phase:** Planning → Implementation  \n**Last Updated:** 2026-04-19\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: Planning & Architecture\n\n| # | Task | Agent | Status |\n|---|------|-------|--------|\n| T1 | @senior-architect — Design system architecture (Next.js app structure, folder layout, data flow) | senior-architect | ⏳ |\n| T2 | @database-schema-designer — Design MongoDB schemas (articles, tags, authors, study_rooms) | database-schema-designer | ⏳ |\n| T3 | @ui-ux-pro-max — Create wireframes for all 5 core pages (Home, Article, Music, Live Study, Search) | ui-ux-pro-max | ⏳ |\n| T4 | @stitch-design — Generate high-fidelity visual mockups (Home, Article detail, Music player, Study room) | stitch-design | ⏳ |\n| T5 | @content-strategy — Define content pillars, topic clusters for CTDL, AI, CS Fundamentals | content-strategy | ⏳ |\n| T6 | @ai-seo — SEO strategy: keywords, structured data schema, content optimization for AI/CTDL topics | ai-seo | ⏳ |\n| T7 | @product-marketing-context — Brand voice, persona definition, ICP | product-marketing-context | ⏳ |\n\n## Phase 2: Implementation — Core Infrastructure\n\n| # | Task | Agent | Status | Depends |\n|---|------|-------|--------|---------|\n| T8 | @senior-frontend — Scaffold Next.js 14 project with TypeScript, Tailwind, shadcn/ui, App Router | senior-frontend | ⏳ | T1 |\n| T9 | @senior-frontend — Implement design system: theme (dark/light), fonts, color tokens, shadcn components | senior-frontend | ⏳ | T8 |\n| T10 | @senior-frontend — Build global layout: Header (nav + search + theme toggle), Footer, Sidebar | senior-frontend | ⏳ | T9 |\n| T11 | @senior-frontend — Implement Home page: Hero section, Featured posts, Category grid, Newsletter CTA | senior-frontend | ⏳ | T10 |\n\n## Phase 3: Blog System\n\n| # | Task | Agent | Status | Depends |\n|---|------|-------|--------|---------|\n| T12 | @senior-frontend — MDX pipeline setup: content layer, syntax highlighting, Mermaid diagrams | senior-frontend | ⏳ | T8 |\n| T13 | @senior-frontend — Article page: reading progress, TOC, author card, related posts, share buttons | senior-frontend | ⏳ | T12 |\n| T14 | @senior-frontend — Category/Tag pages with filtering and pagination | senior-frontend | ⏳ | T12 |\n| T15 | @senior-frontend — Search page: client-side search with Fuse.js or server-side with MongoDB | senior-frontend | ⏳ | T14 |\n| T16 | @senior-backend — Build content API: CRUD for articles, tags, authors (even if file-based for now) | senior-backend | ⏳ | T8 |\n\n## Phase 4: Music Player\n\n| # | Task | Agent | Status | Depends |\n|---|------|-------|--------|---------|\n| T17 | @senior-frontend — Persistent mini-player component (bottom bar, survives navigation) | senior-frontend | ⏳ | T10 |\n| T18 | @senior-frontend — Music library page: playlists (Focus, Sleep, Energize, Study), YouTube/Spotify embeds | senior-frontend | ⏳ | T17 |\n| T19 | @senior-frontend — Audio visualizer (Web Audio API) with fallback | senior-frontend | ⏳ | T17 |\n\n## Phase 5: Live Study Room\n\n| # | Task | Agent | Status | Depends |\n|---|------|-------|--------|---------|\n| T20 | @senior-backend — Socket.IO server setup for real-time presence | senior-backend | ⏳ | T8 |\n| T21 | @senior-frontend — Study room creation + join flow (room code, user display name) | senior-frontend | ⏳ | T20 |\n| T22 | @senior-frontend — Pomodoro timer widget (25/5 cycle, sound notification, session counter) | senior-frontend | ⏳ | T21 |\n| T23 | @senior-frontend — Live participant list: who is in the room, current activity | senior-frontend | ⏳ | T21 |\n| T24 | @senior-frontend — Study goal tracker (daily pages/words studied, streak) | senior-frontend | ⏳ | T23 |\n\n## Phase 6: SEO & Performance\n\n| # | Task | Agent | Status | Depends |\n|---|------|-------|--------|---------|\n| T25 | @seo-audit — Implement next-seo: OG tags, Twitter cards, canonical URLs for all pages | seo-audit | ⏳ | T11 |\n| T26 | @seo-audit — JSON-LD structured data: Article, BreadcrumbList, FAQPage schemas | seo-audit | ⏳ | T13 |\n| T27 | @performance-optimizer — next-sitemap.xml auto-generation, robots.txt, Core Web Vitals audit | performance-optimizer | ⏳ | T26 |\n| T28 | @performance-optimizer — Image optimization: next/image, lazy loading, WebP, blur placeholders | performance-optimizer | ⏳ | T11 |\n\n## Phase 7: Content Seeding\n\n| # | Task | Agent | Status | Depends |\n|---|------|-------|--------|---------|\n| T29 | @realistic-seeder — Seed 5 sample articles: CTDL (1), AI (1), Web Dev (1), DevOps (1), CS Fundamentals (1) | realistic-seeder | ⏳ | T12 |\n| T30 | @realistic-seeder — Seed playlists for music player (YouTube links, descriptions) | realistic-seeder | ⏳ | T17 |\n\n## Phase 8: QA & Final Review\n\n| # | Task | Agent | Status | Depends |\n|---|------|-------|--------|---------|\n| T31 | @senior-qa — Write Playwright E2E tests: home, article, music, study room flows | senior-qa | ⏳ | T24 |\n| T32 | @playwright-pro — Run E2E test suite, verify all critical paths | playwright-pro | ⏳ | T31 |\n| T33 | @code-reviewer — Full codebase review: naming, patterns, security | code-reviewer | ⏳ | T32 |\n| T34 | @security-reviewer — Security audit: CSP, XSS in MDX, CORS, rate limiting on Socket.IO | security-reviewer | ⏳ | T33 |\n| T35 | @senior-devops — Deploy to Vercel: env setup, domain, SSL | senior-devops | ⏳ | T34 |\n\n---\n\n## Dependency Graph\n\n```\nT1 ─┬─ T8 ─ T9 ─ T10 ─ T11 ─ T25 ─ T28\n    │                  └─ T12 ─ T13 ─ T26\n    │                           └─ T14 ─ T15\n    │                           └─ T29\n    │                  └─ T17 ─ T18 ─ T19\n    │                           └─ T30\n    │                  └─ T16\n    │                  └─ T20 ─ T21 ─ T22 ─ T23 ─ T24\n    ├─ T2\n    ├─ T3 ─ T4\n    ├─ T5\n    ├─ T6\n    └─ T7\n\nT26 ─ T27\nT31 ─ T32 ─ T33 ─ T34 ─ T35\n```\n\n## Blockers / Open Questions\n\n1. **Music source:** YouTube embed (free, easy) vs. self-hosted audio (bandwidth cost)? → Decision: YouTube/Spotify embed for Phase 1 ✅\n2. **Live Study backend:** Socket.IO on same Next.js server or separate? → Decision: same server (Next.js custom server) for Phase 1\n3. **Content authorship:** Single author (Lead) or multi-author? → Decision: Single author for Phase 1, multi-author in Phase 2\n4. **GitLab repo:** Create new repo or sub-path in existing? → Decision: New repo `ahv-knowledge-hub`\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":116,"output":1925,"cacheRead":29907,"cacheWrite":1275,"totalTokens":33223,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776569391006,"responseId":"06337f30307d94bf4b7fd19d0b99944f"}}
