{"type":"message","id":"275392fc","parentId":"b93decfb","timestamp":"2026-04-19T04:19:14.142Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Feature branch pushed. Now create the MR via GitLab API.","thinkingSignature":"4d9e534f488a497b9e2f6cf2bc8074cd5d690b49de73811ec309f50423dd2e31"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_jv3cbennvi5e_1","name":"gitlab__gitlab_create_merge_request","arguments":{"project_id":"maiy-hub/maiy-tech-hub","source_branch":"feat/scaffold-initial","target_branch":"develop","title":"feat(maiy): scaffold MAIY Tech Hub — Phase 1 + Phase 2","description":"## MAIY Tech Hub — Initial Scaffold\n\n### What\n- Next.js 14 App Router + TypeScript + Tailwind + shadcn/ui\n- Pages: Home, Articles listing, Article detail, Music, Study, Search\n- SEO: sitemap, robots, JSON-LD Article schema, breadcrumbs\n- Design: Dark/light mode, responsive, smooth UI\n- Music: Mood selector (Focus/Sleep/Energize/Study), YouTube embeds, persistent mini-player\n- Study: Pomodoro timer (25/5), room create/join, participant list, ambient sounds\n- shadcn/ui: button, card, badge, input, dialog, sheet, avatar, separator\n- Socket.IO: server.ts with room events + pomodoro sync\n- Hooks: use-socket.ts, use-pomodoro.ts\n\n### Content\n8 MDX articles across 5 categories:\n- CTDL: Binary Search, Dynamic Programming\n- AI: Linear Regression Python, Neural Network from scratch\n- Web Dev: Next.js App Router, Docker Compose\n- CS Fundamentals: Stack & Heap Memory\n- DevOps: GitHub Actions CI/CD\n\n### Build Status\n- `yarn build` ✅ (12/12 static pages)\n- `yarn lint` ✅ (no warnings)\n\n### Tech Stack\nNext.js 14, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, shadcn/ui, Framer Motion, Socket.IO, MDX\n\n---\n@khuowgn please review and merge."}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":179,"output":425,"cacheRead":137859,"cacheWrite":324,"totalTokens":138787,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"