{"type":"message","id":"694173dc","parentId":"0d5625a9","timestamp":"2026-04-19T04:39:15.147Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Build passed. Let me continue with more improvements while the agents are working. I need to fix more icons and add more features.\n\nLet me check what else needs icon fixes and also add more features to get to 90% completion.\n\nKey remaining tasks:\n1. Fix article card icons\n2. Fix mini-player icons\n3. Fix search page icons\n4. Add more articles (need 15-20 total for a real blog)\n5. Add tags/categories filtering\n6. Improve the article detail page with TOC\n7. Add reading progress bar\n8. Add estimated read time\n9. Add social sharing\n10. Improve the overall UI\n\n\n11. Add OpenGraph images\n12. Add more content\n\nNow I'll tackle these remaining improvements in parallel, starting with the article cards, mini-player, and search functionality, then move on to creating more content and enhancing the article detail page with a table of contents and reading progress indicator.","thinkingSignature":"f821579011e927b4879067633df98dffa816be0cc0b5b523f762c407857b62fc"},{"type":"text","text":"Build ✅ 12/12. Đang chạy 2 agents song song — tiếp tục cải thiện thêm:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_yks6blsrdc4d_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/maiy-tech-hub/components/blog/article-card.tsx"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":98,"output":276,"cacheRead":43216,"cacheWrite":2407,"totalTokens":45997,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776573546869,"responseId":"06338f6bf0b1b878db69b73edb15b046"}}
{"type":"message","id":"2ba2c623","parentId":"694173dc","timestamp":"2026-04-19T04:39:15.199Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_yks6blsrdc4d_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"import Link from 'next/link'\nimport { Clock } from 'lucide-react'\nimport { CATEGORIES } from '@/config/site'\n\nexport interface ArticleSummary {\n  slug: string\n  title: string\n  excerpt: string\n  category: string\n  tags: string[]\n  hero?: string\n  author: string\n  readingTime: number\n  publishedAt: string\n}\n\ninterface ArticleCardProps {\n  article: ArticleSummary\n  variant?: 'default' | 'compact'\n}\n\nexport function ArticleCard({ article, variant = 'default' }: ArticleCardProps) {\n  const cat = CATEGORIES.find((c) => c.slug === article.category)\n\n  if (variant === 'compact') {\n    return (\n      <Link\n        href={`/articles/${article.slug}`}\n        className=\"flex items-start gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-accent transition-colors group\"\n      >\n        {article.hero && (\n          // eslint-disable-next-line @next/next/no-img-element\n          <img\n            src={article.hero}\n            alt={article.title}\n            className=\"w-16 h-16 rounded-md object-cover flex-shrink-0\"\n          />\n        )}\n        <div className=\"min-w-0\">\n          <p className=\"text-xs font-medium text-primary mb-1\">{cat?.label}</p>\n          <h3 className=\"text-sm font-medium line-clamp-2 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors\">\n            {article.title}\n          </h3>\n        </div>\n      </Link>\n    )\n  }\n\n  return (\n    <Link\n      href={`/articles/${article.slug}`}\n      className=\"group flex flex-col rounded-xl border border-border/40 overflow-hidden hover:border-primary/30 hover:shadow-md transition-all\"\n    >\n      {article.hero && (\n        // eslint-disable-next-line @next/next/no-img-element\n        <img\n          src={article.hero}\n          alt={article.title}\n          className=\"w-full h-44 object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500\"\n        />\n      )}\n      <div className=\"p-5 flex flex-col flex-1\">\n        <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\">\n          {cat && (\n            <span\n              className={`px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium rounded ${cat.color} text-white`}\n            >\n              {cat.labelShort}\n            </span>\n          )}\n          <span className=\"flex items-center gap-1 text-xs text-muted-foreground\">\n            <Clock className=\"h-3 w-3\" />\n            {article.readingTime} phút\n          </span>\n        </div>\n\n        <h3 className=\"font-semibold mb-2 line-clamp-2 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors\">\n          {article.title}\n        </h3>\n        <p className=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground flex-1 line-clamp-3\">\n          {article.excerpt}\n        </p>\n\n        <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-border/40\">\n          <span className=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground\">{article.author}</span>\n          <span className=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground\">\n            {new Date(article.publishedAt).toLocaleDateString('vi-VN', {\n              day: 'numeric',\n              month: 'short',\n            })}\n          </span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </Link>\n  )\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776573555177}}
{"type":"message","id":"2df7650b","parentId":"2ba2c623","timestamp":"2026-04-19T04:39:18.938Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Article card looks fine - it uses Lucide Clock icon. Let me check the mini-player, search page, and article detail page for more emoji usage.","thinkingSignature":"5d97a48fe0f7ba2f03bf9b8c987ef3b165117a66678d5b6b1d079535f619e295"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ujxcphlsotz2_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/maiy-tech-hub/components/music/mini-player.tsx"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":829,"output":84,"cacheRead":45375,"cacheWrite":560,"totalTokens":46848,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776573555209,"responseId":"06338f74d61ee46316890758cd121c2f"}}
{"type":"message","id":"d6877806","parentId":"2df7650b","timestamp":"2026-04-19T04:39:19.025Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ujxcphlsotz2_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"'use client'\n\nimport Link from 'next/link'\nimport { Pause, Play, SkipForward, Volume2, X } from 'lucide-react'\nimport { useMusic } from '@/providers/music-provider'\nimport { useEffect, useState } from 'react'\n\nexport function MiniPlayer() {\n  const { currentTrack, isPlaying, pause, resume, skipNext } = useMusic()\n  const [visible, setVisible] = useState(false)\n\n  useEffect(() => {\n    if (currentTrack) setVisible(true)\n  }, [currentTrack])\n\n  if (!visible || !currentTrack) return null\n\n  return (\n    <div className=\"fixed bottom-0 left-0 right-0 z-50 border-t border-border/40 bg-background/95 backdrop-blur supports-[backdrop-filter]:bg-background/80\">\n      <div className=\"container flex h-16 items-center gap-4\">\n        {/* Track info */}\n        <div className=\"flex items-center gap-3 min-w-0 flex-1\">\n          {currentTrack.coverUrl && (\n            // eslint-disable-next-line @next/next/no-img-element\n            <img\n              src={currentTrack.coverUrl}\n              alt={currentTrack.title}\n              className=\"w-10 h-10 rounded object-cover flex-shrink-0\"\n            />\n          )}\n          <div className=\"min-w-0\">\n            <p className=\"text-sm font-medium truncate\">{currentTrack.title}</p>\n            <p className=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground truncate\">\n              {currentTrack.artist}\n            </p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        {/* Controls */}\n        <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n          <button\n            onClick={isPlaying ? pause : resume}\n            className=\"p-2 rounded-full bg-primary text-primary-foreground hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors\"\n            aria-label={isPlaying ? 'Tạm dừng' : 'Phát'}\n          >\n            {isPlaying ? (\n              <Pause className=\"h-4 w-4\" />\n            ) : (\n              <Play className=\"h-4 w-4 ml-0.5\" />\n            )}\n          </button>\n\n          <button\n            onClick={skipNext}\n            className=\"p-2 rounded-full hover:bg-accent transition-colors\"\n            aria-label=\"Bài tiếp theo\"\n          >\n            <SkipForward className=\"h-4 w-4 text-muted-foreground\" />\n          </button>\n\n          <Link\n            href=\"/music\"\n            className=\"hidden sm:flex p-2 rounded-full hover:bg-accent transition-colors\"\n            aria-label=\"Mở trang nhạc\"\n          >\n            <Volume2 className=\"h-4 w-4 text-muted-foreground\" />\n          </Link>\n        </div>\n\n        {/* Close */}\n        <button\n          onClick={() => setVisible(false)}\n          className=\"p-1 rounded hover:bg-accent transition-colors\"\n          aria-label=\"Đóng\"\n        >\n          <X className=\"h-4 w-4 text-muted-foreground\" />\n        </button>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  )\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776573559003}}
