{"type":"message","id":"544cc7a5","parentId":"17583600","timestamp":"2026-04-19T04:43:48.576Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Build is running. While waiting, let me think about what else I need to add to get to 90% completion. \n\nCurrent features done:\n1. ✅ Pages: Home, Articles listing, Article detail, Music, Study, Search, About\n2. ✅ Category pages\n3. ✅ Dark/light mode\n4. ✅ SEO: sitemap, robots, JSON-LD, breadcrumbs\n5. ✅ Reading progress bar\n6. ✅ Social share (Twitter, FB, copy link)\n7. ✅ Table of contents (auto-extract)\n8. ✅ Back to top button\n\n\n9. ✅ Copy code button\n10. ✅ Sort articles (newest/oldest/reading time/a-z)\n11. ✅ Search modal with Cmd+K shortcut\n12. ✅ Newsletter form\n13. ✅ Responsive design\n14. ✅ Music: mood selector, YouTube embeds, mini-player\n15. ✅ Study: Pomodoro timer, room create/join, participants, ambient sounds\n16. ✅ Lucide icons throughout\n17. ✅ 8 MDX articles\n\nStill need to build out the remaining features to hit that 90% target.\n\n18. ✅ SEO revalidation API route\n19. ✅ WebSite schema\n20. ✅ Breadcrumb schema\n21. ✅ E2E tests (in progress)\n22. ⏳ Improved MDX renderer (currently using basic regex)\n23. ⏳ Sitemap should include all article URLs\n24. ⏳ OpenGraph for all pages\n25. ⏳ Keyboard shortcut hints (Cmd+K)\n26. ⏳ Reading time estimate display\n27. ⏳ Better error/404 page\n28. ⏳ Loading skeletons\n29. ⏳ Favicon generation\n\nNow I need to create the custom 404 page and set up loading skeletons for better UX while pages load.","thinkingSignature":"57aff7bc731ce9a6795458f935d0abe1934d35a5f5ada992e0b0e6ad28c2855c"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_66fckjln1nes_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/maiy-tech-hub/app/not-found.tsx","content":"import Link from 'next/link'\nimport { Home, Search, ArrowLeft } from 'lucide-react'\n\nexport default function NotFound() {\n  return (\n    <div className=\"container flex flex-col items-center justify-center min-h-[60vh] py-20 text-center\">\n      <div className=\"mb-6\">\n        <span className=\"text-8xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-500 to-purple-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent\">\n          404\n        </span>\n      </div>\n      <h1 className=\"text-2xl font-bold mb-3\">Trang không tìm thấy</h1>\n      <p className=\"text-muted-foreground mb-8 max-w-md\">\n        Trang bạn đang tìm kiếm có thể đã bị xóa, đổi tên, hoặc tạm thời không khả dụng.\n      </p>\n      <div className=\"flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3\">\n        <Link\n          href=\"/\"\n          className=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg bg-primary text-primary-foreground font-medium hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors\"\n        >\n          <Home className=\"h-4 w-4\" /> Về trang chủ\n        </Link>\n        <Link\n          href=\"/articles\"\n          className=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg border border-border hover:bg-accent transition-colors font-medium\"\n        >\n          <ArrowLeft className=\"h-4 w-4\" /> Danh sách bài viết\n        </Link>\n        <Link\n          href=\"/search\"\n          className=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg border border-border hover:bg-accent transition-colors font-medium\"\n        >\n          <Search className=\"h-4 w-4\" /> Tìm kiếm\n        </Link>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  )\n}\n"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_66fckjln1nes_2","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/maiy-tech-hub/app/loading.tsx","content":"export default function Loading() {\n  return (\n    <div className=\"container py-12\">\n      {/* Article grid skeleton */}\n      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6\">\n        {[1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6].map((i) => (\n          <div key={i} className=\"rounded-xl border border-border/40 overflow-hidden\">\n            <div className=\"h-44 bg-muted animate-pulse\" />\n            <div className=\"p-5 space-y-3\">\n              <div className=\"h-3 bg-muted rounded w-1/3 animate-pulse\" />\n              <div className=\"h-5 bg-muted rounded w-3/4 animate-pulse\" />\n              <div className=\"h-4 bg-muted rounded w-full animate-pulse\" />\n              <div className=\"h-4 bg-muted rounded w-2/3 animate-pulse\" />\n              <div className=\"flex justify-between pt-2 border-t border-border/40\">\n                <div className=\"h-3 bg-muted rounded w-1/4 animate-pulse\" />\n                <div className=\"h-3 bg-muted rounded w-1/4 animate-pulse\" />\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        ))}\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  )\n}\n"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_66fckjln1nes_3","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/maiy-tech-hub/components/blog/article-card-skeleton.tsx","content":"'use client'\n\nexport function ArticleCardSkeleton() {\n  return (\n    <div className=\"rounded-xl border border-border/40 overflow-hidden animate-pulse\">\n      <div className=\"h-44 bg-muted\" />\n      <div className=\"p-5 space-y-3\">\n        <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n          <div className=\"h-5 w-16 bg-muted rounded-full\" />\n          <div className=\"h-3 w-16 bg-muted rounded\" />\n        </div>\n        <div className=\"h-5 bg-muted rounded w-3/4\" />\n        <div className=\"h-4 bg-muted rounded w-full\" />\n        <div className=\"h-4 bg-muted rounded w-2/3\" />\n        <div className=\"flex justify-between pt-2 border-t border-border/40\">\n          <div className=\"h-3 w-20 bg-muted rounded\" />\n          <div className=\"h-3 w-16 bg-muted rounded\" />\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  )\n}\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":101,"output":1554,"cacheRead":56055,"cacheWrite":241,"totalTokens":57951,"c