{"type":"message","id":"492258f4","parentId":"870886a7","timestamp":"2026-04-19T04:45:07.329Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The develop branch has been pushed. Now let me continue with Phase 5 - implementing more features. Let me think about what else needs to be done to reach 90% completion.\n\nLet me list the current features:\n1. ✅ Home page with hero, featured article, categories, recent posts\n2. ✅ Articles listing with sort controls\n3. ✅ Article detail with TOC, reading progress, social share, tags, related posts\n4. ✅ Category pages\n5. ✅ Music page with mood selector, YouTube embeds, mini-player\n6. ✅ Study page with Pomodoro timer, room create/join, ambient sounds\n\n\n7. ✅ Search page\n8. ✅ About page\n9. ✅ Dark/light mode\n10. ✅ SEO (sitemap, robots, JSON-LD schemas, breadcrumbs)\n11. ✅ Reading progress bar\n12. ✅ Back to top button\n13. ✅ Copy code button\n14. ✅ 404 page\n15. ✅ Loading skeletons\n16. ✅ Lucide icons throughout\n17. ✅ Newsletter form\n18. ✅ E2E tests\n19. ✅ Keyboard shortcuts\n\nNow I'm thinking through what would push this to 90% completion. I should add a proper MDX renderer instead of relying on regex parsing, implement open graph metadata for all pages, and consider a few other polish features like enhanced search functionality, better SEO configuration, and documentation.\n\nLooking at what's left, I'm adding a reading time indicator, improving the article detail page layout, creating a proper error boundary, setting up a manifest for PWA support, and making the home page more dynamic with featured content sections. For the MDX renderer specifically, I need to install the necessary packages and set up the content library to properly handle MDX files with components and syntax highlighting.\n\nLet me start by installing `@next/mdx` and `react-syntax-highlighter` since these are critical for rendering code in articles properly.","thinkingSignature":"a5a6fc662e3d92ef93d6a6781d7980856fbb12b9f82499e7707c9940d408a408"},{"type":"text","text":"develop synced ✅. Tiếp tục Phase 5 — MDX renderer + polish:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_45zc5idfptpd_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/maiy-tech-hub && yarn add @next/mdx @mdx-js/react remark-gfm rehype-highlight rehype-slug rehype-autolink-headings 2>&1 | tail -5","yieldMs":20000,"timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":1047,"output":516,"cacheRead":60965,"cacheWrite":314,"totalTokens":62842,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776573894179,"responseId":"063390c724e7e31af7afcb4038c92dbe"}}
