{"type":"message","id":"205a94c8","parentId":"19190c61","timestamp":"2026-04-19T05:01:52.570Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me give the Lead a comprehensive status update.","thinkingSignature":"e5763d50f2f3c3ed3176a6af30b89ef8a8e38a89d36885a425445853d62da1b9"},{"type":"text","text":"**MAIY Tech Hub — Hoàn thành ~90%** 🎉\n\nDev server đang chạy: http://localhost:3000\n\n---\n\n### Tổng quan features đã build:\n\n| Module | Features |\n|---|---|\n| **Content** | 10 MDX articles (CTDL×2, AI×2, Web Dev×4, DevOps×1, CS×1), category pages, related articles, sort/filter |\n| **Music** | Mood selector (Focus/Sleep/Energize/Study), YouTube embeds, persistent mini-player |\n| **Study** | Pomodoro timer (25/5), room create/join, ambient sounds (Rain/Café/Library) |\n| **SEO** | Sitemap, robots, WebSite schema, Article schema, Breadcrumb schema, ISR revalidation API, OG tags |\n| **UX** | Reading progress bar, table of contents, copy-code button, social share, back-to-top, loading skeletons, error boundary |\n| **Design** | Dark/light mode, Lucide icons (không emoji thô), responsive, PWA manifest |\n| **E2E** | 16 Playwright tests (home, articles, music, study, search, SEO) |\n| **Build** | 20/20 pages ✅ |\n\n---\n\n### Git — đúng quy trình:\n```\ndevelop ← feat/scaffold-initial (MR !1)\ndevelop ← feat/icon-refresh  \ndevelop ← feat/mdx-renderer  \ndevelop ← feat/pwa-polish  \ndevelop ← (latest) ✅ pushed\n```\n\n---\n\n### Còn lại ~10%:\n- Socket.IO server cần deploy để Study rooms thực sự real-time\n- Comments system\n- Analytics\n- Real content từ Lead/contributors\n\n**Repo:** https://gitlab.com/maiy-hub/maiy-tech-hub\n\nLead xem thử http://localhost:3000 — có gì cần chỉnh sửa hoặc bổ sung gì không?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":73,"output":446,"cacheRead":98263,"cacheWrite":660,"totalTokens":99442,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"to