{"type":"message","id":"ac96161f","parentId":"2daa3bd8","timestamp":"2026-04-19T05:27:06.378Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The dev server is running. Let me give a final summary to Lead.","thinkingSignature":"8138fbf00e408731e264db7788062bea74de6df89dde67c2cd0768a4d7a5f42d"},{"type":"text","text":"**MAIY Tech Hub — ~95% hoàn thành** 🎉\n\nDev server: http://localhost:3000\n\n---\n\n### Features mới thêm vừa xong:\n\n| Feature | Chi tiết |\n|---|---|\n| **Hero Animation** | Gradient orbs bay lơ lửng, gradient text animated, stagger entrance với framer-motion |\n| **Featured Badge** | Bài viết đầu tiên có badge \"Nổi bật\" màu vàng ⭐ |\n| **Articles Filter** | Search + category pills + sort — tất cả trong 1 component |\n| **Search Page** | Keyboard nav, category filter, result cards thay vì grid |\n| **Newsletter API** | `/api/newsletter` với Zod validation — sẵn sàng kết nối Mailchimp/Resend |\n| **Newsletter Form** | Real API call với loading spinner + error states |\n| **Build** | 28/28 pages ✅ |\n\n---\n\n### Tổng kết toàn bộ:\n\n- **Pages:** 28 trang (Home, Articles×3, Music, Study, Search, About, Contribute, Admin×4, + error/loading/not-found)\n- **Content:** 10 MDX articles (CTDL×2, AI×2, Web Dev×4, DevOps×1, CS×1)\n- **Admin:** Login, Dashboard, Articles CRUD, Article Editor\n- **Animations:** Hero, article cards hover, scroll reveals, Pomodoro transitions\n- **SEO:** Sitemap, robots, JSON-LD schemas, ISR, breadcrumbs\n- **Real-time:** Socket.IO study rooms với participant sync\n- **E2E:** 16 Playwright tests\n- **Dev server:** http://localhost:3000 đang chạy\n\n### Còn lại ~5%:\n- Comments system (cần backend/DB)\n- Analytics integration (Vercel Analytics, Google Analytics)\n- Performance/Core Web Vitals optimization\n\n**Repo:** https://gitlab.com/maiy-hub/maiy-tech-hub"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":81,"output":472,"cacheRead":143025,"cacheWrite":618