{"type":"message","id":"273f97d4","parentId":"927df9a6","timestamp":"2026-04-19T05:32:51.400Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me add a README.md to the project root with all the information.","thinkingSignature":"200c372ec622e8b6725d884240e77e4a3cef5e574720e39d860d16f17072ea55"},{"type":"text","text":"**Phase 4: README + SPEC update:**\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_88ja2gjayxhv_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/maiy-tech-hub/README.md","content":"# MAIY Tech Hub\n\nNền tảng blog chia sẻ kiến thức CNTT chuẩn chỉnh bằng tiếng Việt.\n\n**Live:** https://maiytechhub.com\n\n## Tính năng\n\n- 📝 **Bài viết MDX** — Code thật, giải thích dễ hiểu, syntax highlighting\n- 🎵 **Relaxation Zone** — Nhạc thư giãn theo mood (Focus, Sleep, Energize, Study)\n- 📚 **Phòng học Live** — Pomodoro timer + real-time collaboration\n- 🔍 **Tìm kiếm thông minh** — Fuzzy search với Fuse.js\n- 🌙 **Dark/Light mode** — Tự động theo hệ thống\n- 📱 **Responsive** — Mobile-first design\n- 🔎 **SEO** — Sitemap, robots, JSON-LD schema, breadcrumbs\n- ⚡ **Fast** — Next.js 14 App Router, ISR\n\n## Tech Stack\n\n- **Framework:** Next.js 14 (App Router)\n- **Language:** TypeScript\n- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui\n- **Animations:** Framer Motion\n- **Content:** MDX + next-mdx-remote\n- **Search:** Fuse.js\n- **Real-time:** Socket.IO\n- **Testing:** Playwright (E2E)\n\n## Cấu trúc thư mục\n\n```\n├── app/                    # Next.js App Router pages\n│   ├── articles/           # Article listing + detail\n│   ├── music/              # Music relaxation zone\n│   ├── study/             # Live study room + Pomodoro\n│   ├── search/             # Fuzzy search\n│   ├── admin/              # Admin panel\n│   └── api/                # API routes\n├── components/             # React components\n│   ├── blog/               # Article components\n│   ├── layout/            # Header, Footer\n│   ├── music/              # Music components\n│   ├── seo/                # SEO schema components\n│   ├── admin/              # Admin components\n│   └── ui/                 # shadcn/ui base components\n├── content/articles/       # MDX articles\n├── hooks/                  # Custom React hooks\n├── lib/                    # Utilities\n├── config/                 # Site configuration\n└── public/                 # Static assets\n```\n\n## Phát triển\n\n```bash\n# Cài đặt dependencies\nyarn install\n\n# Chạy dev server\nyarn dev\n\n# Build production\nyarn build\n\n# Chạy tests\nnpx playwright test\n```\n\n## Đóng góp\n\n1. Fork repo\n2. Thêm bài viết MDX vào `content/articles/[slug].mdx`\n3. Tạo Pull Request\n\nXem thêm: [Hướng dẫn đóng góp](./app/contribute/page.tsx)\n\n## Chủ đề bài viết\n\n- **CTDL** — Cấu trúc dữ liệu & Giải thuật\n- **AI** — Trí tuệ nhân tạo & Machine Learning\n- **Web Dev** — Phát triển web\n- **DevOps** — DevOps & Cloud\n- **CS Fundamentals** — Kiến thức cơ sở\n\n## License\n\nMIT — Kiến thức vì cộng đồng.\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":114,"output":849,"cacheRead":150850,"cacheWrite":381,"totalTokens":152194,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776576755093,"responseId":"06339bf4ec66f0ea7ef060cb573b018b"}}
