{"type":"message","id":"86a51e86","parentId":"0b1da9a0","timestamp":"2026-04-19T07:21:21.063Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ykhsr5dk13ep_1","toolName":"image","content":[{"type":"text","text":"This screenshot shows a mobile browser on the **MAIY Tech Hub** website displaying a **404 error page**.\n\n### What the user is seeing\n- A large **“404”** in purple.\n- Vietnamese text: **“Trang không tìm thấy”** = **“Page not found.”**\n- Explanation below:\n  - **“Trang bạn đang tìm kiếm có thể đã bị xóa, đổi tên, hoặc tạm thời không khả dụng.”**\n  - Meaning: **“The page you are looking for may have been deleted, renamed, or temporarily unavailable.”**\n\n### Visible UI elements\nAt the top:\n- Site logo/name: **MAIY Tech Hub**\n- Icons for:\n  - **Search**\n  - **Theme/night mode** (crescent moon)\n  - **Menu** (hamburger icon)\n\nMain action buttons:\n- **“Về trang chủ”** = **Go to homepage**\n- **“Danh sách bài viết”** = **Article list**\n- **“Tìm kiếm”** = **Search**\n\nAdditional helper text:\n- **“Bạn có thể tìm thấy thông tin hữu ích ở trang chủ hoặc tìm kiếm bài viết.”**\n- Meaning: **“You can find useful information on the homepage or by searching for articles.”**\n\n### Browser / device status\n- It appears to be on an **iPhone** in Safari.\n- Time shown: **14:20**\n- Battery is very low: **9%**\n- The browser bar at the bottom says **“Not Secure”**, indicating the page may be served without HTTPS or with a certificate/security issue.\n\n### Summary\nThe user has landed on a **missing page / broken link** on the MAIY Tech Hub site, and the site is offering navigation options to return home, view posts, or search."}],"details":{"model":"ahvholding/AHV-Holding-TroLy","image":"/root/.openclaw/media/inbound/file_7---56660c24-ada2-4422-abde-3622170b3b43.jpg","attempts":[]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776583281038}}
{"type":"message","id":"2cbf54f9","parentId":"86a51e86","timestamp":"2026-04-19T07:21:34.377Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is showing me a screenshot of the 404 page. They're on their iPhone at 14:20 (which means 7:20 AM UTC+7). The 404 page is showing, meaning they tried to access a page that doesn't exist. They also note \"Not Secure\" — this means the site is not served over HTTPS on localhost.\n\nBut they might be testing from their phone and can't access localhost. The \"Not Secure\" and the fact they're on iPhone at a specific time suggests they might be trying to access from a different network.\n\nAlso, this might be a general screenshot showing the 404 - it could mean the article pages ARE showing 404 for some reason, not just the 404 page itself.\n\n\nThe 404 page itself looks good and the theme toggle is working, so the real issue is likely that their phone can't reach localhost since it's only accessible on the machine running the server. They probably need to either be on the same network or expose it with a tunneling service like ngrok. The \"Not Secure\" warning confirms they're not on HTTPS, which is expected for localhost.","thinkingSignature":"ed1957ac926c3a6ad85eaa3909696151188b0f88f75ab2f47469b0f5970db0b0"},{"type":"text","text":"Lead đang truy cập từ iPhone — mình đoán `localhost:3000` không truy cập được từ điện thoại vì server đang chạy trên máy chủ.\n\n**Vấn đề:** Không phải lỗi code mà là network — Lead đang ở ngoài, không truy cập được localhost.\n\n**Giải pháp — chạy ngrok để public:**\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_t30h5v8kshor_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"which ngrok || (which npx && npx ngrok --version 2>/dev/null) || echo \"no ngrok\"","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":508,"output":400,"cacheRead":158748,"cacheWrite":540,"totalTokens":160196,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"c