{"type":"message","id":"5a4164b8","parentId":"fa7e1675","timestamp":"2026-04-19T07:35:38.889Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lead wants to add real-time communication features to the Study room: camera, voice chat, text chat, and screen sharing. This is a complex feature that requires:\n\n1. WebRTC for camera/voice/screen sharing\n2. WebSocket (Socket.IO) for real-time text chat\n3. STUN/TURN servers for NAT traversal\n\nLet me implement this step by step. I'll use:\n- `socket.io` for signaling and text chat\n- Browser WebRTC API for camera/voice/screen\n- Simple approach without heavy external dependencies\n\nLet me plan this properly:\n\n1. **Text Chat**: Extend Socket.IO to support chat messages in study rooms\n\n\n2. **WebRTC Setup**: Use Socket.IO as the signaling mechanism, leveraging browser APIs directly\n3. **Camera/Mic**: MediaDevices API to access camera and microphone\n4. **Screen Share**: Screen capture API\n\nNow I need to build out the UI components—a chat panel, video grid, and control bar—then update the study room page to tie everything together. I'll start with the WebRTC service and work up through the components.","thinkingSignature":"b0af05811762dd0f666505938d4efa1a8f654e859866559a41315277a0780501"},{"type":"text","text":"Lead muốn Study Room có camera, voice, chat, screen share. Đây là tính năng phức tạp — mình sẽ implement từng phần.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gi9hd13ovj07_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/prompt-optimizer/skills/prompt-optimizer/SKILL.md","limit":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":0,"output":334,"cacheRead":169689,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":170023,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776584121414,"responseId":"0633b8bb43a041b43719f3655700ac2f"}}
